   Date:   Sat Sep 25 08:15:13 2010 +0000
   
       beef up the test suite
       
       We need to test server <-> client interaction
       more thoroughly since some systems don't implement
       everything right.
   
   commit 460e6b025896dee64b39d194d4c1a536129654de
